This is the longpolling server I use for the mining pools I run on
bitparking.com for various virtual currencies based on bitcoin.

See [1] for a description of how to use this program.

The server is written in the ATS programming language [2].

[1] http://sourceforge.net/mailarchive/message.php?msg_id=28562589
[2] http://www.ats-lang.org
